Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:10.48,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{The gates have finally opened.}Brány se konečně otevřely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:13.58,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Though I am eager to \Nreach the land I long for,}Ačkoliv dychtím dosáhnout té země po které toužím,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:17.49,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{if I leave with regrets, it will\N put a damper on my departure.}pokud odejdu s výčitkami tak bych odcházel se splínem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:18.95,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{This guy!}Ten chlápek!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:20.08,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Wait, Kotetsu.}Počkej, Kotetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:22.59,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's me that Kark wants.}Jsem to já koho Kark chce.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:25.45,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You guys head to the Foundation's HQ.}Vy běžte do Nadačního HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:26.25,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{But...}Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:28.93,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{We can't leave you!}Nemůžeme tě opustit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:29.87,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Just go!}Prostě jdi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.55,0:02:32.42,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro's right.}Chihiro má pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:36.67,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{If we delay here, Tokyo will be consumed.}Pokud se tu zdržíme, Tokio bude pohlceno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:38.66,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm going.}Já půjdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:41.59,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{I won't be able to face Inuki otherwise.}Nemohla bych se podívat Inukimu do tváře.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.98,0:02:43.16,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Kotecchan.}Kotíku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:46.60,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-san, be careful.}Chihio, buď opatrný.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.85,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I will. You, too.}Budu. Vy taky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:50.34,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Later, Chihhi.}Později, Chihhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:52.06,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{We've got this.}Zvládneme to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:56.71,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Thanks for waiting, Kark.}Díky, žes počkal, Karku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:00.22,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't worry about it.}Nedělej si starosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:04.83,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{The god of death is not so boorish\N that he rushes final farewells.}Bůh smrti není tak nezdvořilý, aby spěchal na konečné rozloučení.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:06.86,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't plan to die.}Neplánuju zemřít.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:10.08,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{There's someone I want to see.}Je někdo koho chci vidět.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:12.58,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Regrets cloud the soul.}Lítostivý oblak duše.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:16.59,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{The least I can do is beautifully\N embellish it with my requiem.}Nejmenší co mohu udělat je přikrášlit ho svou pohřební písní.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:21.59,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{The serpent god of death that\N swallows the world, Jörmungandr.}Hadí bůh smrti polykající světy, Jörmungandr.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:24.10,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You... Again?}Zase... ty?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:27.72,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{The Lord of Vermilion demands\N thousands of offerings.}Vermilionský lord vyžaduje tisíce nabídek.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:34.31,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{You are to blame for everything,\N Kamina Chihiro.}Za všechno jsi vinnen, Kamina Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:40.38,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Listen to the grievances of the people.}Poslyš lidský nářek.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:42.82,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{This is your redemption.}Toto je tvé vykoupení.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.34,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I already told you.}Už jsem ti to řekl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:52.91,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I won't ask for forgiveness.}Nežádám odpuštění.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:55.58,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I will shoulder all the blame.}Ponesu všechnu vinu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:05.50,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{The soul of the one closest\N to the Lord of Vermilion...}Duše toho, který je nejblíže Vermilionskému lordu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:07.54,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{shall be mine.}bude má.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:12.69,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{What is that?}Co je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:15.19,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{That's the Foundation HQ?}To je Nadační HQ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:18.46,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Looks like an ordinary mansion to me.}Vypadá to jako obyčejné panské sídlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:23.00,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Grumman and Professor Mitsuki\N once conducted their research there.}Grumman a Profesorka Mitsuki tam jednou prováděli výzkum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:27.35,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Everything is in motion. They are\N trying to bring about the end.}Vše je v pohybu. Snaží se dosáhnout do konce.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:29.01,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{You're sure this is it?}Jsi si jistá, že je to ono?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:30.15,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Kotecchan!}Kotíku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:34.71,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{If you want answers, ask difficult questions.}Pokud chcete odpovědi, zeptejte se obtížných otázek.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:38.12,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{How truly scholarly.}Jak skutečně vědecké.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:42.01,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{She acts like this doesn't affect her.}Chová se jako by se jí to netýkalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:46.32,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Densuke, go!}Jdi, Densuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:55.90,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Second summer president, Tsubaki the Red,\N also known as Manazuru Tsubaki,}Druhá letní prezidentka, Rudá Tsubaki, také známá jako Manazuru Tsubaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.15,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{is on the way!}je na cestě!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:04:59.12,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Nice!}Hezky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:06.66,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{What a waste.}Jaká škoda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:10.15,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{No blade can pierce Jormungandr's scales.}Žádná čepel neprobodne šupiny Jormungandra.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.15,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Revel and exalt.}Veselte se a oslavujte.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:53.74,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Death is kind and precious. \N Its beauty is arresting.}Smrt je milá a vzácná. Její krása je strhující.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:00.68,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Did I lose consciousness?}Ztratil jsem vědomí?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:04.30,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's me?}To jsem já?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:06.47,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Yes, you.}Ano, ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.55,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Could it be?}Mohlo by to být?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.92,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{It's all right. Not yet.}Vše je v pořádku. Ještě ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:16.55,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I see. I wouldn't want to die\N without accomplishing my goal.}Chápu. Nechtěl bych zemřít, aniž bych splnil můj cíl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:20.23,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{But it's finally my turn, huh?}Ale konečně jsem na řadě, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:22.98,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{How would you like to die?}Jak by sis přál zemřít?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:29.65,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You're the one responsible\N for my prophetic dreams.}Ty jsi ta, která je zodpovědná za mé prorocké sny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:32.64,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You've been taunting me with illusions.}Posmíval ses mi s iluzemi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:36.41,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{They were not illusions. \NThey're your memories.}To nebyly iluze. To byly tvoje vzpomínky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:39.90,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Everything is like a play.}Vše je jako hra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:43.21,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{It is performed countless\N times over and over again,}Provádí se nesčetněkrát znovu a znovu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:45.84,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{though each time, the cast\N and ad-libbing changes.}ačkoli pokaždé se mění obsazení a improvizace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:49.38,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{However, the conclusion never changes.}Závěr se však nikdy nezmění.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:52.39,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{These are my memories?}To jsou mé vzpomínky?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:54.72,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{In other plays.}V jiné hře.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:59.02,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{The dreams are a warning, to prevent you\N from committing the same mistakes.}Sny jsou varováním, které vám zabrání v tom, abyste se dopustili stejných chyb.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:02.76,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Why? Why only me?!}Proč? Proč pouze já?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:08.74,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{When one curtain fell, you raised another.}Když padla jedna opona, zvedl jsi další.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:13.55,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't know why, but that's the reason.}Nevím proč, ale to je důvod.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:16.14,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I know why.}Já vím proč.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:19.34,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{In other words, I've never\N been forgiven in any play.}Jinými slovy, mi nebylo odpuštění v žádné jiné hře.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:21.85,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I thought I would be in the next one.}Myslel jsem, že by mohlo být v příštím.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.81,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's pathetic.}Je to patetické.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:29.55,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Even the worst play has its merits.}Dokonce i nejhorší hra má své zásluhy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:35.35,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{This is the first time so many vessels\N of Heroic Lineage have survived.}Tohle je poprvé co tolik nádob hrdinsé linie přežilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:37.95,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Can I change how it ends?}Mohu změnit jak to skončí?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.77,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{That's up to you.}To je na tobě.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:44.18,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Densuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:45.40,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{How dare you!}Jak se opovažuješ!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.94,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{No, Tsubaki-chan!}Ne, Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:49.42,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{There's no end to them.}Neexistuje pro ně žádný konec.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:51.55,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Koume-san, go on without us.}Koume, jdi napřed bez nás.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:52.33,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Cože?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:53.95,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{You're right.}Máš pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:56.13,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{What are you talking about?}O čem to mluvíte?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:07:58.42,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{If we delay, Tokyo will be in trouble, right?}Budeme-li zpoždění, Tokyo bude mít problémy, ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:02.87,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{We're counting on you, Koume-san!}Spoléháme na tebe, Koume!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:08.07,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{You guys had better not die!}Radši byste neměli umírat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:11.33,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{We've drawn the short straw.}Vytáhli jsme krátkou slámu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:15.66,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Really? I'm pretty happy to be alone with you.}Opravdu? Jsem docela rád, že se s tebou o samotě.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:21.28,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Kotecchan? Is this the time \Nto say that kind of stuff?}Kotíku? Je to čas říkat takové věci?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:22.35,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Sorry.}Promiň.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:24.82,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm not great at reading the room.}Nejsem dobrý v čtení atmosféry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:27.20,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{But I don't want to have any regrets.}Ale nechci ničeho litovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:30.11,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{There's no need to apologize.}Není se za co omlouvat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:32.11,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm all fired up, now!}Teď jsem úplně nabuzená!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:35.16,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{You can tell me all about it later.}Můžeš mi o všem říct později.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:37.60,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{I will. I promise I'll protect you!}Řeknu. Slibuju, že tě ochráním!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:41.87,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Coming through!}Projdi skrz!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:44.75,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Kill them, Chiyu.}Zab je, Chiyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:48.78,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{If I am not here to manage it, the odds\N it will run out of control increase.}Pokud nejsem tady, abych to zvládla, pravděpodobnost, že se vymkne kontrole se zvýší.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:50.38,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{That's fine.}To je v pořádku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:54.90,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{If they close the gate before\N I see Mitsuki, I'll lose everything.}Pokud zavřou bránu předtím, než uvidím Mitsuki, ztratím všechno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:09:00.29,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Please, my beloved daughter.}Prosím, má milovaná dcero.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:02.25,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{Sophist.}Sofisto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.39,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{What was that?}Co to bylo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:09.50,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{You attempt to manipulate us\N by pretending to love us.}Pokusíš se námi manipulovat předstíráním, že nás miluješ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:13.37,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{Me. Yuri. Even Professor Mitsuki.}Mě. Yuri. Profesorku Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:18.20,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{The love you speak of is for yourself only.}Láska o které mluvíš je pouze pro tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:20.16,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Quiet, doll!}Mlč, loutko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:21.33,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{Yes.}Ano.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:28.59,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{You used your and Professor Mitsuki's\N DNA to create me as a substitute for her.}Použil jsi DNA sebe a profesorky Mitsuki k vytvoření mě jako její náhrady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:30.70,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{That's how I know.}Tak to vím.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:36.34,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{I am both Professor Mitsuki\N and Shiraki Aldo Grumman.}Jsem obojí profesorka Mitsuki i Shiraki Aldo Grumman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:40.80,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{You can only love yourself.}Dokážeš milovat jen sebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:44.42,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Y-You're wrong. I loved Mitsuki.}Mýlíš se. Já miluji Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:50.29,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{One more thing: Professor\N Mitsuki never loved you.}Jedna věc navíc: Profesorka Mitsuki tě nikdy nemilovala.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:53.51,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{I can tell.}To mohu říct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:59.65,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{You can open the gate,\N but she won't be waiting for you.}Můžeš otevřít bránu, ale čekat na tebe nebude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.65,0:10:01.35,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{There's no way she would.}Není způsob jak by mohla.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:05.48,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{She simply wishes to return to her family.}Jen se chce vrátit ke své rodině.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:08.08,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Are you Mitsuki?}Jsi Mitsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:10.88,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Bastards!}Šmejdi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:14.82,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{I refuse to believe this.}Odmítám tomu uvěřit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:16.76,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Huh?}Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:19.53,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't believe it.}Tomu nevěřím.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:21.03,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{I refuse to believe this.}Odmítám tomu uvěřit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:26.37,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't believe you!}Nevěřím ti!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:34.02,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{You're alive, defect.}Jsi naživu, defekt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:36.22,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{You haven't changed, Chiyu.}Nezměnila jsi se, Chiyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:39.89,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{You've been looking down your nose\N at me since our time at the orphanage.}Shrnuješ nos už od doby co jsme byli v sirotčinci.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:40.78,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{Really?}Opravdu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:44.16,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Move, Chiyu! Don't blame me if you get hurt!}Uhni Chiyu! Neobviňuj mě pak, když se ti něco stane!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:46.91,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{You bitch!}Ty mrcho!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:50.90,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{This is all because of\N a foolish man's obsession.}To všechno je kvůli posedlosti tohoto ubohého muže.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:53.86,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{There's no reason for me to\N fulfill my duty anymore,}Neexistuje žádný důvod, proč bych už měla plnit svou povinnost,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:58.01,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{but a foolish woman's curiosity\N wants to see how it ends.}ale zvědavost žalostné ženy chce vidět, jak to skončí.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:05.41,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{That is the reason I fight.}To je důvod proč bojuju.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:10.58,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Moment by moment, the wheel of fate turns.}Okamžik za okamžikem, kolo osudu se otáčí.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:13.19,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Are you saying we're all going to die?}Chceš říct, že všichni zemřeme?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:15.52,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{It could end like this.}Mohlo by to tak skončit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:19.18,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{I'd simply go watch a new play.}Mohla bych se jít jednoduše dívat na novou hru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:22.18,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{They entrusted me with their dying wishes.}Svěřili mi svá poslední přání.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:27.70,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Inuki-san, Kakihara-san,\N Kurokami-san, Shoko-san.}Inuki, pan Kakihara, Kurokami, Shoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:30.54,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Even Aoi Jun fought desperately.}Dokonce Aoi Jun bojoval zoufale.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:34.91,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{They weren't just following \Nthe destiny laid out for them,}Nechtěli jen sledovat osud, který jim byl určen,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:36.70,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{they were fighting back.}bojovali.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:39.72,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll never give up.}Nikdy se nevzdám.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:43.75,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{What will you do by changing the script?}Co uděláš změnou skriptu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:45.23,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I...}Já...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:46.81,Shinsou main,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Live.}Žij.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:49.49,Shinsou main,AERO,0000,0000,0000,,{Live.}Žij.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:50.56,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Live.}Žij.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:51.58,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{Live.}Žij.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:52.50,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Live.}Žij.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:53.38,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{Live.}Žij.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:58.19,Shinsou main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,{Live, Chihiro.}Žij, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:03.08,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll live!}Já budu žít!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:07.58,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{The winds are changing.}Větry se mění.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:11.08,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll fight until the very end.}Budu bojovat až do samého konce.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:13.43,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I will change my fate!}Změním svůj osud.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:18.64,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Cože?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:31.85,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Impossible.}Nemožné.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:35.84,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{He's incinerating the god that\N brings about the end?}Spaluje boha, který přináší konec?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:42.31,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{Not bad.}To není špatný.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:46.05,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Lord of Vermilion.}Vermilionský lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:49.91,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You're all that's left, Kark.}Jsi poslední co zbylo, Karku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:53.64,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Burning gods and destroying demons...}Pálení bohů a ničení démonů...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:56.57,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{These are no longer the deeds of humans.}To už nejsou skutky lidí.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.67,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{To what end have you \Nabandoned your humanity?}Do jaké míry jste opustil své lidství?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:01.75,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You're wrong, Kark.}Mýlíš se, Karku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:04.10,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{People's wishes...}Lidská přání...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:08.75,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{The wishes of the people important\N to me have made me stronger.}Přání lidí, kteří jsou pro mě důležití, mě posilnily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:13.21,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Your existence is an affront to the gods of death.}Vaše existence je urážkou bohů smrti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:15.52,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{You will never be forgiven.}Nikdy ti nebude odpuštěno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:18.90,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{I will not forgive you! Kamina Chihiro!}Já ti neodpustím! Kamina Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:25.65,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,Amadeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:32.22,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{My hands! My hands!}Mé ruce! Mé ruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:35.37,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{My piano! My piano!}Mé piáno! Mé piáno!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:39.38,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{This is what you deserve, Kark.}To je co jsi zasloužíš, Karku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:42.12,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{I was so close to his land.}Byl jsem tak blízko k jeho Zemi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:46.31,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Someone play the piano for me.}Někdo zahrajte na piáno pro mě.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:50.48,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Play for me the ultimate requiem.}Zahrajte dokonalou pohřební píseň.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:13:59.29,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{This is starting to get tough.}Začíná jít do tuhého.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:01.23,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Is this the end?}Je tohle konec?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:04.44,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Huh?}Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:07.04,Shinsou main,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{You disgrace yourself, Tsubaki.}Styď se, Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:10.28,Shinsou main,SURUGA,0000,0000,0000,,{And you call yourself a member\N of the Guardian State?}A to jsi říkáš strážkyně?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:12.81,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Julijuli? {Why?}Proč?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:14.29,Shinsou main,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{It goes without saying.}Na to nemusím ani odpovídat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:18.56,Shinsou main,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{The Guardian State exists to\N protect the world from evil spirits.}Strážci existjí pro ochranu světa před zlými duchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:21.45,Shinsou main,SURUGA,0000,0000,0000,,{We're just doing our job.}Jen děláme svou práci.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:23.70,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Thanks for saving us.}Díky za naší záchranu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:25.55,Shinsou main,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't thank us.}Neděkuj nám.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:27.45,Shinsou main,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{Destroy all demons!}Znič všechny démony!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:30.07,Shinsou main,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{Exorcise them, Gabriel!}Vymítej je, Gabrieli.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:32.22,Shinsou main,SURUGA,0000,0000,0000,,{Crush them,}Rozdrť je, Lia Fáil!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:35.64,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't underestimate me!}Nepodceňuj mě!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:37.35,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{This is pointless.}To je zbytečné.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:39.98,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{I've already calculated all your movements.}Propočítala jsem všechny tvé pohyby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.27,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Is that right?}Fakt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:42.77,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Take this!}Zkus tohle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:45.73,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.18,0:14:50.70,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't assume everything will\N always go according to plan.}Nepředpokládej, že vše bude vždy podle plánu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:55.58,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{There are people in this world\N who challenge the impossible!}Na tomto světě jsou lidé, kteří vyzývají nemožné!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:00.01,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{How dare you...}Jak se opovažuješ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:01.88,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{You defect.}Defekte.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:04.56,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{There's no such thing as a defective life.}Neexistuje nic takového jako vadný život.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:09.10,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Life is obligated to struggle\N until the very end.}Život je povinen bojovat až do samého konce.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:12.39,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{That's why it's worth saving!}To je důvod proč stojí za záchranu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:20.39,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{That's probably what Inuki would say.}To je asi to, co by Inuki řekl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:22.58,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Stop the machine.}Zastav ten stroj.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:24.15,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{I can't.}Nemůžu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:28.44,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{Enough.}To stačí.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:34.16,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{Now that I can't control \Nthe machine, it's all over.}Nyní když nemůžu ovládat stroj, je po všem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:42.33,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{It's her punishment for mocking me.}To je její trest za to, že se mi posmívala.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:44.84,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{No one can deceive me!}Nikdo mě nemůže oklamat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:49.85,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm coming for you, Mitsuki!}Jdu si pro tebe Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:52.84,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{Let me give you a hand!}Dovol mi podat ti ruku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:57.63,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:01.60,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{Idiot!}Debile!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:06.89,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Did they succeed?}Uspěli?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:08.82,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{No, they failed.}Ne, selhali.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:12.43,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Now that it's beyond control,\N the gate will continue to expand.}Nyní, když je mimo kontrolu, brána se bude dále rozšiřovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:14.56,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Eventually it will consume the world.}Nakonec to pohltí celý svět.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:15.99,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{No...}Ne...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:19.89,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Not yet. I won't give up yet.}Ještě ne. Ještě se nevzdám.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:21.38,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{There must be a way!}Musí být způsob!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:24.04,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Tell me, Dux! Please!}Řekni, Dux! Prosím!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:27.04,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{There is one thing.}Je tu jedna věc.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:30.25,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{The Lord of Vermilion.}Vermilionský lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:36.73,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{The Lord of Vermilion has the\N power to create new worlds.}Vermilionský lord má sílu tvořit světy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:39.55,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{As the candidate closest to becoming it,}Jako nejbližší kandidát na post,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.55,0:16:41.60,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{it would be possible\N for you to erase the gate.}by to mohlo být možné, aby jsi zničil bránu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:43.88,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{However...}Nicméně...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:48.19,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.81,0:16:52.35,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Where are you going, Chihiro-kun?}Kam se chystáš, Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:58.28,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Step aside, Yuri.}Ustup stranou, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:00.29,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{You won't answer me?}Neodpovíš mi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:03.69,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Then I'll say it.}Potom ti to řeknu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.24,0:17:06.29,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{You're planning to enter the gate.}Plánuješ vstoupit do brány.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:11.27,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{The Lord of Vermilion could erase the gate.}Vermilionský lord mohl zničit bránu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:15.49,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{However, that requires countering\N one power with another...}To však vyžaduje vyvažování jedné síly s jinou ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:17.72,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{in exchange for your life.}výměnou za tvůj život.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:20.51,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{How do you know that?}Jak to víš?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:24.09,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Because someone was kind enough to tell me...}Protože někdo byl tak laskav a řekl mi to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:26.10,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{that you would die.}že bys mohl umřít.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:30.61,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{That's right, Yuri. Save Chihiro.}Správně, Yuri. Zachraň Chihira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:32.57,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{Kill him!}Zab ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:34.10,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Why?!}Proč?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.71,0:17:37.87,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Why do you have to throw away your life?!}Proč chceš zahodit svůj život?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:42.29,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I know why I was told to live!}Vím, proč mi bylo řečeno abych žil!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.78,0:17:45.85,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{As long as I'm alive, I can keep using my life!}Dokud budu naživu, mohu dál používat svůj život!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:48.84,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{That makes no sense! I don't understand!}To nedává smysl! Nechápu to!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:50.28,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't want to understand!}Nechci to chápat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:52.30,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm sorry.}Promiň.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:55.18,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{You've changed.}Změnil ses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:58.18,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{You'd never leave me without saying anything!}Nikdy bys mě neopustil, aniž by mi nic neřekl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:00.68,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Please, Yuri! Let me—}Prosím, Yuri! Nech mě—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:01.80,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I won't let you go!}Nenechám tě projít!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:08.14,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll never be forgiven anyway.}Nikdy mi nebude odpuštěno.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:11.85,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I killed Cerdid-san with these hands.}Těmahle rukama jsem zabila Cerdid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:15.72,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You're wrong! You were\N forced to defend yourself.}Mýlíš se! Byla jsi donucena použít sílu k sebeobraně.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:17.86,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{It doesn't change the fact that I killed her.}To nemění nic na faktu, že jsem jí zabila.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:23.08,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{So I will protect you instead.}Takže tě ochráním.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:25.33,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I won't let you die!}Nenechám tě zemřít!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:28.25,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Stop, Yuri!}Přestaň, Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:32.91,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{There's no turning back for me now.}Pro mě není cesty zpět.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:36.13,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{But I can at least save you.}Ale můžu tě alespoň zachránit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:40.51,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Why? How did this happen?}Proč? Jak se to stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:43.55,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I was reunited with you.}Opět jsem se s tebou shledala.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:46.16,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{We drank hot cocoa in the sun together.}Pili jsme horké kakao za slunečného dne.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.53,0:18:48.85,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{It made me happy.}Dělalo mě to šťastnou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:51.59,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I just wanted to keep doing that!}Chtěla jsem to dělat dál!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:53.98,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-kun!}Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:55.40,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:10.20,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-kun...}Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:24.33,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I could never kill the most\N important person in my life.}Nikdy bych nemohl zabít nejdůležitější osobu v mém životě.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:27.14,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{You haven't changed.}Nezměnil jsi se.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:31.27,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-kun, you haven't changed.}Chihiro, ty jsi se nezměnil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:35.64,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I... What have I been doing?}Já ... Co jsem to dělala?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:39.37,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm sorry, Chihiro-kun.}Omlouvám se, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:41.20,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm sorry.}Omlouvám se.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:43.53,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's fine, Yuri.}To je v pořádku, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.27,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-kun.}Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:52.90,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm sorry, Yuri. I...}Omlouvám se. Yuri. Já...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.83,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I won't stop you.}Nezastavím tě.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:19:57.32,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Take me with you.}Vezmi mě sebou.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:19:58.26,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Cože?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:03.71,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't have much strength left, but\N I think I can provide a little assistance.}Nemám moc síly, ale myslím, že ti mohu poskytnout trochu pomoci.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.71,0:20:07.37,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{No. I can't do that. You have to stay.}Ne. Nemohu to udělat. Musíš zůstat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:08.31,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't leave me!}Neopouštěj mě!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:10.88,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Please.}Prosím.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:15.90,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I can't live without you anymore.}Už bez tebe nemohu žít.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:18.74,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:26.74,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Aren't you scared, Yuri?}Bojíš se, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:28.45,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{No, I'm with you.}Ne, jsem s tebou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:31.91,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't let go of my hand.}Nepouštěj mou ruku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:34.97,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Stay with me forever.}Zůstaň se mnou napořád.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:36.28,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I will.}Zůstanu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:43.77,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{In a beautiful sky without conflict,\N we'll walk together forever.}Na krásné obloze bez konfliktu budeme navždy společně chodit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.73,0:20:46.60,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Like Romeo and Juliet?}Jako Romeo a Julie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:49.63,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't you like it?}Nelíbí se ti?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:52.60,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't know what to say. It's a tragedy.}Nevím co říct. Je to tragédie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:56.44,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{We're different.}My jsme jiní.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:20:59.04,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You're right.}Máš pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:03.74,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Maybe I'll try saying my own one-liner.}Možná, bych mohl zkusit říct svou vlastní hlášku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:05.41,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{What is it?}Co je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:07.67,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:10.91,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Give me the courage to do this.}Dej mi odvahu to udělat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:13.83,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-kun!}Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:19.22,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Wait!}Počkej!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:21.23,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{No!}Ne!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:23.65,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm sorry, Yuri.}Promiň, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:26.89,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I can't take you with me.}Nemůžu tě vzít sebou.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.89,0:21:28.76,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Why? Why not?!}Proč? Proč ne?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:30.61,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Live, Yuri.}Žij, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:33.84,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Live for me.}Žij pro mě.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:37.06,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You're more important to me\N than anyone or anything.}Jsi pro mě důležitější, než kdokoliv jiný.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:38.46,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-kun!}Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:41.38,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Promise me, Yuri.}Slib mi, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:44.72,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Live.}Žij.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:47.75,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Yes.}Ano.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:51.70,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Yes. I promise.}Ano. Slibuju.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:53.48,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Thank you.}Děkuju ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.48,0:21:56.96,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Now I'll finally be...}Teď budu konečně...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:21:59.99,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-kun!}Chihiro!
